code: /**  * Returns the IP addresses of {@code hostname}, in the order they will be attempted by OkHttp. If  * a connection to an address fails, OkHttp will retry the connection with the next address until  * either a connection is made, the set of IP addresses is exhausted, or a limit is exceeded.  */ List<InetAddress> lookup(String hostname) throws UnknownHostException.
